name: chip-diagram-generator
description: "Use when generating chip module diagrams (block diagrams, timing diagrams, FSM diagrams). Triggers on '框图', '时序图', '状态机图', 'diagram', 'mermaid', 'wavedrom', '架构图'. Generates module block diagrams, timing diagrams and state machine diagrams."
